    "en": {
      "title": "8 crores to educate the people",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The attention of the COPE committee has been drawn to an incident where an amount of four crore fifty eight lakh rupees has been paid to the staff of the Public Utilities Commission under 11 types of allowances.",
        "In addition to this, information has been revealed that more than eight crore rupees have been spent on public awareness programs, i.e. 49 percent of the total cost of the entire operation, said the COPE committee.",
        "This information was revealed when the heads of the commission were called before the COP committee to inquire about the affairs of the council."
      ],
